      "text": "（あそこにいるのは……天動さん？　そういえば）\n（TRINITYAiLEはトリだったな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Is that Tendo-san over there? That’s right‚)\n(TRINITYAiLE is giving the final performance of this event.)",
        "id": ""
