      "text": "はい、さっき終わった所で……\n休憩、していました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we just finished…\nI was taking a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.405530400725382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEのみなさんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about the other members of TRINITYAiLE?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.67238049904506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
