      "text": "優は出演する別グループのリハーサルを見ています\nすみれは楽屋で宿題を片付けるそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu is watching the rehearsal of another group that’s performing.\nSumire is finishing up her homework in the waiting room.",
        "id": ""
